sourcesContent: import React from "react"; import { Box, Typography, Container, Grid, Card, CardContent, Avatar, Link } from "@mui/material"; import { FaShieldAlt, FaUsers, FaLightbulb, FaGlobe } from "react-icons/fa"; const teamMembers = [ { name: "Disha Dutta", avatar: "D", link: "https://www.linkedin.com/in/disha-dutta-748579275/" }, { name: "Mridula Shrivastava", avatar: "M", link: "https://www.linkedin.com/in/mridula-shrivastava-724072253/" }, { name: "Kumari Sonam", avatar: "K", link: "https://www.linkedin.com/in/kumari-sonam-693314251/" }, { name: "Muskan Atray", avatar: "M", link: "https://www.linkedin.com/in/muskan-a-723032252/" }, { name: "Praavinya Chaturvedi", avatar: "P", link: "https://www.linkedin.com/in/praavinya-chaturvedi/" }, ]; const AboutScamify = () => { return ( {/* Title */} About Us - Team SCAMIFY {/* What is Scamify */} What is SCAMIFY? With the rapid growth of the internet, digital fraud has become more sophisticated, making it harder for users to differentiate between genuine and fraudulent platforms. Thus, WE, a team of passionate B.Tech IT students, developed SCAMIFY, a project aimed at identifying and preventing online scams. {/* Our Motive */} Our Motive SCAMIFY is driven by our commitment to creating a safer digital space. Our platform acts as a protective tool, helping individuals make informed decisions while browsing. {/* Features */} {[ { title: "User-Friendly", icon: , desc: "No technical knowledge required; accessible to all." }, { title: "Effective", icon: , desc: "Uses structured methods to detect scams and warn users." }, { title: "Preventive Tool", icon: , desc: "Aims to educate and protect users before they fall victim." }, { title: "Digital Safety", icon: , desc: "Helps create a well-informed online community." }, ].map((feature, index) => ( {feature.icon} {feature.title} {feature.desc} ))} {/* Meet the Team */} Meet Our Team {teamMembers.map((member, index) => ( {member.avatar} {member.name} ))} {/* Our Vision */} Our Vision SCAMIFY is more than just a project—it’s a step towards a safer internet. Our goal is to continuously improve through research and innovation, empowering individuals to protect themselves online. {/* Stay Safe */} Stay Safe with SCAMIFY In a world where cyber threats evolve constantly, SCAMIFY ensures you can browse the internet with confidence. ); }; export default AboutScamify;
